Dear <%= @user.first_name %>,

The following <%= @opportunities.count == 1 ? "opportunity is" : "opportunities are" %> awaiting your review:

<% @opportunities.each do |opportunity| %>
- <%= opportunity.display_title %>
  Submitted by: <%= opportunity.creator&.full_name || opportunity.submitter_name %>
  Submitted on: <%= l opportunity.created_at.to_date, format: :long %>
  Review at: <%= admin_opportunity_url(opportunity) %>

<% end %>
Regards,

Pineapple
